{"tid":602817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰開打】環時總編：中國會限大豆進口 打擊特朗普票倉","createTime":"2018-03-23T08:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a14689b2fa9521b42ac2eec683baf22a3bcfa2cf","tid":602817,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521793041_32fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521793041_32fa.jpg&h=81d6de39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰拉開戰幔，官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進加入叫陣，於微博稱農業州為共和黨票倉，大豆為特朗普「門牙」，確信中國會迅速限制美國大豆進口，「堅決打掉特朗普的這顆門牙，讓他豁著嘴去見選民」。胡錫進形容美國關稅措施為「野蠻方案」，同時中國不想打貿易，不過敢戰才能止戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180323/57985575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985575&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=c5d7710c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985575&h=5c2716c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180323/57985575</a>"},{"pid":"71ced2089f57328be35a7ef513f3c1afea37391c","tid":602817,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"人地打到你骨折，你打到人甩條毛咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ce1ec8e14c1cb957522b143126053daffdfbea","tid":602817,"uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"【中國高度依賴食物進口】<br />\n【美國大豆便宜 品質更遠勝國產】<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》提出，中國在貿易上的即時反制措施，是限制美國大豆入口，中國的底氣在那裡呢?<br />\n<br />\n2017年中國總共入口了9000萬噸大豆，當中有3000萬噸來自美國。但首先要問，為何要入口美國大豆呢?答案是價錢，美國大豆的入口價，比國產的平了35%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，內地業內人士指出，美國大豆質量完全可以KO國產大豆，可以製造很多副食品。<br />\n<br />\n其實中國總體糧食市場高度依賴進口，過去十年不斷上升，去年的入口糧食依存度已超過兩成。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指出，內地糧食生產受制於水資源成本上漲、種子價格上升了一倍、人力和土地成本不斷上升。<br />\n<br />\n有經濟學者指出，過去十年如果不是靠平價的入口糧食平衡市場，食品價格早已全面急升，通脹數字遠比官方公布的嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1671269276350885/?hc_ref=ARTAsFQhseEKvAc8KSzenzTflNxpUrl5yIzQMNavbQMib3ifKPl71o-en13ix3a5ElA&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1671269276350885%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARTAsFQhseEKvAc8KSzenzTflNxpUrl5yIzQMNavbQMib3ifKPl71o-en13ix3a5ElA%26fref%3Dnf&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=2a847042\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1671269276350885/?hc_ref=ARTAsFQhseEKvAc8KSzenzTflNxpUrl5yIzQMNavbQMib3ifKPl71o-en13ix3a5ElA&amp;fref=nf</a>"},{"pid":"1f5095e850837da50fcd9273ac4b0889b144fe71","tid":602817,"uid":117651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"習大大：為加強香港係一帶一路嘅角色，立即擔當起進口美國大豆嘅重任，盼望香港珍惜一帶一路嘅機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9619b397db50c5f5d1c22768533ca81528b33ae","tid":602817,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"黎香港轉口唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460ddbaeafca94b8957cc25da16fc3843a1b4c13","tid":602817,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5095e850837da50fcd9273ac4b0889b144fe71","tid":602817,"uid":117651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"習大大：為加強香港係一帶一路嘅角色，立即擔當起進口美國大豆嘅重任，盼望香港珍惜一帶一路嘅機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"港共政府搞限豆令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4738bac62e049825af8d52d933a345d58e29749","tid":602817,"uid":8873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"開頭依幾日官方傳媒梗係吹水話會同佢打貿易戰有乜有乜<br />\n<br />\n實情相邊度有得打。美國睇住你中國嚟食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你先叫支那人唔俾用蘋果手機 專用國貨 睇吓班支那九幾多人會？ <br />\n<br />\n2-30年前啲人未見過外國商品得<br />\n而家你俾佢見過外國商品就唔可能返轉頭"}]}